  "description": {
    "en": {
      "provenance": "imported",
      "value": "To assist in the development of a well considered legal framework that meets the needs and aspirations of the Nepali people and conforms to international standards\r\n    Provide key stakeholders with information and technical advice on electoral issues related to the constitution and election and political party laws\r\n    To build the capacity of targeted stakeholders on the electoral legal framework\r\n    Support and strengthen the EC of Nepal as an independent electoral management body, including support to a potential revised structure of the Commission subsequent to the ratification of the new constitution\r\n    To facilitate rapid conduct of elections under the new constitution"
    },
